title: Shoulder Surgery Recovery
content: Had shoulder surgery in March 2022. Recently given clearance to expand range of motion. Week 9 post-op PT session included 11 shoulder exercises. These exercises are beneficial even if not recovering from surgery.

title: Shoulder Exercises
content: Isometric Shoulder Extension, Isometric Shoulder Flexion, Isometric Shoulder External Rotation, Assisted Flexion/Supination with Core Activation and Diaphragmatic Breathing, Ipsilateral Rotation With Banded Hip and Shoulder Facilitation, Bilateral Banded External Rotation (3 hand positions), Kickstand RDL with External Rotation Isometric the Shoulder, Reverse Lunge with Isometric Row, Isometric Cuff walk-outs (Increases load tolerance without motion to the joint)

title: Rotator Cuff Exercises
content: Rotator Cuff Eccentrics, Rotator Cuff Eccentric with Drop sets
